### 13.3 `google.script.run` bridge endpointleri (index/admin)

Not: Bunlar dogrudan `routeAction` degil, web UI'nin server function cagrilaridir.

| UI | Bridge ornekleri |
|---|---|
| `index.txt` | `authGetSession`, `authLogout`, `authSendOtp`, `authVerifyOtp`, `getEquipmentData`, `getStudiosListForUi`, `getStudioWeeklyGridBridge`, `checkStudioCalendarBridge`, `reservationsCreateBridge`, `studioReservationsCreateBridge`, `getMyBookingsBridge`, `cancelReservationBridge`, `contactCreateBridge`, `ticketCreateBridge` |
| `admin.txt` | `checkAdminAccessBridge`, `getPendingCount`, `getPendingRequests`, `processRequest`, `getTrafficData`, `adminProcessPartialCheckout`, `adminProcessPartialCheckin`, `adminCreateStudioReservation`, `adminUpdateStudioReservation`, `adminDeleteStudioReservation`, `getAdminStudioWeeklyGrid`, `getAdminReservationHistory`, `syncGoogleCalendarsToStudiosBridge`, `adminTicketsListBridge`, `adminTicketApproveBridge`, `adminTicketRejectBridge`, `getAdminReportsSummaryBridge`, `adminSpecialAccessUpsertBridge` |

### 13.4 Hata davranisi

- Bilinmeyen action -> `Unknown action: <action>`
- Role disi erisim -> `Access denied.`
- Admin bridge'lerde yaygin cevap: `{ error: 'Yetkisiz.' }`

